Package gov.va.chir.model

Class DocumentHeader_Type

java.lang.Object
org.apache.uima.jcas.cas.TOP_Type
org.apache.uima.jcas.cas.AnnotationBase_Type
org.apache.uima.jcas.tcas.Annotation_Type
gov.va.chir.model.DocumentHeader_Type
public class DocumentHeader_Type
extends org.apache.uima.jcas.tcas.Annotation_Type
This header contains meta-data about the doucment, and could be extended to cover the kinds of meta-data that the HL7 CDA document header contains about a clincial record, such as who was the author, provider, patient, when the service happened, when it was reviewed, and the like. Updated by JCasGen Thu Aug 18 18:15:19 EDT 2022
